{"parentUuid":"8d978754-8c69-4cb1-8f6a-cf3f0204963c","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"eca00838-5098-4dde-983a-34e68a423bb3","agentId":"aa3971c3406bc34d2","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GaP8SizUpCpDtQCVgBuE9Q","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Meterly\n2\t\n3\t## Stack\n4\t- Cloud environment: AWS (ECS Fargate + RDS PostgreSQL + ALB), Terraform under infra/\n5\t- Language/runtime: Python 3.12\n6\t- Framework(s): FastAPI\n7\t- Data stores: PostgreSQL\n8\t- Migration tool: Alembic\n9\t- Cloud / IaC: AWS + Terraform\n10\t- Auth provider: API keys (Argon2id-hashed at rest), per-key rate limiting — no third-party IdP\n11\t- Observability: CloudWatch + X-Ray + Sentry (release-tagged)\n12\t- Packaging / runtime: container (Docker) — justified: deploys through the ECS canary path\n13\t\n14\t## How to run / build / test\n15\t- Start: `uvicorn src.main:app --port 8000` (smoke check expects HTTP 200 at `http://localhost:8000/health`)\n16\t- Test:  `pytest --cov=src --cov-branch`\n17\t- Migrate: `alembic upgrade head` (run before deploying; also run locally after pulling schema changes)\n18\t- Deploy: CI on merge — see docs/pipeline-deployment-targets.md (build-provenance → deploy.yml chain)\n19\t\n20\t## Frontend design source\n21\t- Design source: none (API only)\n22\t\n23\t## Conventions\n24\t- Module layout: src/ package (src/main.py app entry), facade modules per code-standards defaults\n25\t- Test locations: tests/ as test_*.py\n26\t\n27\t## What \"done\" means\n28\t- Smoke check passes, security report clean, tests pass at >= 85% coverage,\n29\t  docs updated for touched directories, PR description written.\n30\t\n31\t<!--\n32\t  REMEMBER per project: the smoke-check.sh hook reads Start/health values above.\n33\t  Set them here, or export SMOKE_START_CMD / SMOKE_HEALTH_URL, or (frontend-only)\n34\t  swap in the build-check variant of smoke-check.sh from the spec.\n35\t-->\n36\t"}]},"uuid":"6ba326a4-9f1e-4b73-bb84-fe0d9e8d750e","