{"parentUuid":"5d1d4ff5-eaea-4217-b9f2-2d3072d133a7","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"aa3971c3406bc34d2","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011CcqAxtxs1BD8CYaqPwKtr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011dVaG9mRttEdgjEHCPDkaG","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test\\docs\\system_architecture.md","old_string":"# Meterly — system architecture (first feature)\n\n## Overview\n\nMeterly ingests metered usage events and serves aggregated per-customer/metric\ncounters. Two authenticated HTTP endpoints, one PostgreSQL database, one Redis\nrate-limit store, running as a Docker container on ECS Fargate behind an ALB.\n\n```\nClient --HTTPS+API key--> ALB --> FastAPI (ECS Fargate, >=2 tasks)\n                                     |-- Tier-1 (IP) / Tier-2 (api_key_id) throttle --> Redis\n                                     |-- bound-parameter SQL, RLS-scoped -------------> RDS PostgreSQL\n                                     |-- DB credential fetch ------------------------> Secrets Manager\n                                     |-- traces/logs/errors -------------------------> CloudWatch/X-Ray/Sentry\n```","new_string":"# Meterly — system architecture\n\n## Overview\n\nMeterly ingests metered usage events, serves aggregated per-customer/metric\ncounters, and enforces admin-set per-customer, per-metric usage caps\n(\"quotas\"). Three authenticated HTTP endpoints, one PostgreSQL database, one\nRedis rate-limit store, running as a Docker container on ECS Fargate behind\nan ALB.\n\n```\nClient --HTTPS+API key--> ALB --> FastAPI (ECS Fargate, >=2 tasks)\n                                     |-- Tier-1 (IP) / Tier-2 (api_key_id) throttle --> Redis\n                                     |-- bound-parameter SQL, RLS-scoped -------------> RDS PostgreSQL\n                                     |-- DB credential fetch ------------------------> Secrets Manager\n                                     |-- traces/logs/errors -------------------------> CloudWatch/X-Ray/Sentry\n```"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":661,"cache_read_input_tokens":246871,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":661,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcqAxsAiALekAX7fZdNKR","attributionAgent":"implementation","type":"assistant","uuid":"3780f307-83c3-42df-9199-c8d5abe34a9b","timestamp":"2026-07-08T19:51:25.634Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"d6fd840f-4c15-4ec4-8e2b-f4a42b2cbb1a","version":"2.1.204","gitBranch":"feature/metric-quotas"}
